if an anesthesiologist or a surgeon is distracted by the technology in the operating room, that can create a problem.<EOS>
in the operating room, it’ s not just the phone, although that’ s sometimes present, but you have all the displays and technology.<EOS>
each one of those are creating alarms that creates this whirl of noise, and alerts and distractions that compete for the anesthesiologist’ s and the surgeon’ s attention.<EOS>
so i’ ve been reading about how the modern worker, let’ s say in the u. s.<EOS>
