we all may have multiple pieces of communication software, multiple pieces of productivity software, and so on.<EOS>
can you talk about that, what seems to be a relatively low- stakes environment— the workplace in a marketing firm or whatever— but how our attention is being carved up during the course of the day?<EOS>
